# Cloudflare Pages redirect rules.
# Format: <source> <destination> <status>[!]
# The trailing ! forces the rule even when a real file exists at the path.

# Master rate sheet — competitor / data-leak protection.
# Order matters: rewrite for /login/ (Access-gated) MUST come before the public 404!.
/login/rates.xlsx  /rates.xlsx  200
/rates.xlsx        /            404!
